put server in front of stage
sip client connects with correct creds
sip client fails to connect with incorrect creds
sip client fails to connect with incorrect user
conneced sip client can send outgoing call
connected sip client can receive incoming call

bring down stage
sip client fails to connect with correct creds
bring up stage
sip client connects with correct creds

put two servers in front of stage
sip client connects to either with correct creds
conneced sip client can send outgoing call
connected sip client can receive incoming call

connect sip client with correct creds, shut down server, bring up server, sip client reconnects
